Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.24,0:01:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.51,0:01:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个和尚说的河边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.05,0:01:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…发带？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗 你真的还活着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.23,0:01:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇的声音与桔梗的唇瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了 我的死期也就是你的死期
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.21,0:02:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是抱着对你的怨恨死去的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵魂永远停滞在那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.22,0:02:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你活在这个世上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.95,0:02:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就无法得到救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡着了吗？桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.51,0:02:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像…很悲伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.48,0:02:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你穿过了我的结界吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结…结界？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这么个东西吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召集那些少女亡魂的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是那样的话 请你让她们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没在一起吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉他…说要来找你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.11,0:03:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 犬夜叉正想到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是犬夜叉的什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:20.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体…动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.29,0:03:26.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…绊脚石
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收集亡魂的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.64,0:03:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有结界…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗就在这里面…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗 真的是你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我动不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是来救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是来见我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你捣乱的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捣乱？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你还是想杀了犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你误会了 桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有人故意让你们相互怨恨的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死你的根本不是犬夜叉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的表情好像在说我应该高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,致我于死地的真凶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人死了 我就能复活吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死者的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是重新得到生命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.21,0:04:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不可能实现的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 死者也有能够实现的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.45,0:05:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把那个最不该把我忘记的人的心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最不该把你忘记的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指犬夜叉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在期待我的死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来他对我们的战斗还留有悔恨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他去后悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不会让他忘了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也绝不会让时间前进
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就能在静止的时间里获得生命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就能永远活在那家伙的心里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在犬夜叉也总是想着你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.43,0:05:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样还不够吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉是喜欢着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直都在他心里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样还不够吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.71,0:05:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.21,0:05:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是带着对彼此的怨恨离别的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的那种温暖的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会增加我们的怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有比让两个人的心结合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.32,0:06:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更能增加怨恨这种感情的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他爱我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就爱我的怨念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我 则深陷其中 去爱着他的心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 你太不讲理了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.04,0:06:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样实在太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 你快告诉桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉她你们的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为被奈落骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉看不到我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:07:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你在收集少女的亡魂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个泥土和骨灰造就的虚假身躯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不填满灵魂就无法行动自如
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 你很厌恶我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我靠着对你的怨恨支撑自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收集死者的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而继续待在这世上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别…别胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你在怨恨我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来没有忘记过你！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…犬夜叉一直对桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.83,0:07:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像…有点寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.27,0:07:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉被抢走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:08:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.34,0:08:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是跟犬夜叉在交往…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.51,0:08:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你变成什么样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.08,0:08:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不会觉得厌恶或憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我现在却有可能亲手杀了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 自从遇到你以后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.44,0:08:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不再是个巫女了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成了一个普通的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我活着的时候就一直想像这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…一下就接受了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 他当然会很自然地接受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.46,0:09:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我离他们这么近干嘛呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像个傻瓜一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.07,0:09:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 害我都哭了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊 我太没用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人怀念的桔梗的味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟以前一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不同的是已经不再温暖了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已然死去的身体如此冰冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此悲伤…如此寂寞…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经无法回到那个时侯了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我想再这样待一会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本无法拯救桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.83,0:09:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果无法为她做任何事 干脆…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆就这样让时间静止…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.23,0:09:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的…想让时间静止吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我什么都不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.74,0:09:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要跟…桔梗在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…我快看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会妨碍你们的啦 快放开我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会自动消失的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们两个听到没有？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 我不会再让你走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我一起下地狱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.10,0:10:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他渐渐被拉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 你在做什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不快点逃走！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.38,0:10:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 他已经被夺去意识了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗 你可以听到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.15,0:10:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说犬夜叉想跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是他没有说要陪你去死啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉跟你不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.62,0:10:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要打倒50年前设计陷害你们的奈落啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.56,0:10:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉最希望做的是活着战斗下去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为犬夜叉是想为你报仇啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.19,0:11:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算他能复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这副身躯也不会再复活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其带着对我的思念活着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如跟我一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.21,0:11:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你所希冀的 是一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是因为犬夜叉失去了意识
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他才不会跟你一起走呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我离犬夜叉远点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不准你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰犬夜叉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个女人…又要夺走我的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.15,0:12:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在亡魂全部脱离这副身躯之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.39,0:12:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 犬夜叉 快点醒过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 犬夜叉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.91,0:12:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 快点醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 犬夜叉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇的声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇…她在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这种地方干什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你又在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我？我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.72,0:13:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女人…比我还重要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 桔梗 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.11,0:13:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 你不要忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我与你亲吻的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是虚假的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.38,0:14:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在生什么气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能一个人去找四魂之玉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能…没办法跟你一起去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在胡说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你能看到四魂碎片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:42.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个人肯定不行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因为那样吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之所以需要我 只是因为那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像在说废话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.15,0:15:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 就当你刚才什么都没听到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能因为我孤独一人待在陌生的世界吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得有点寂寞了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是…有我在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.93,0:15:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能陪着你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看不见我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:20.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从头到尾都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.72,0:15:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…你让我一个人待会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部是什么啊…全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇…那时候我做了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 戈薇 告诉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说全部就是全部啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都在特等席看得清清楚楚的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？找到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:16:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这个地方干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你有没有看到戈薇？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个倒下的姿势好眼熟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来戈薇小姐没事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.99,0:16:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说戈薇现在精神的不得了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？阿枫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你害怕我这个姐姐吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.25,0:16:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…我听说姐姐您从悬崖顶上摔了下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以为您已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我已经是死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我还对这世间充满了迷恋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您还想要犬夜叉的性命吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才我跟犬夜叉见过面了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过没能取他性命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.95,0:17:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我 阿枫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我你所知道的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于奈落的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.47,0:17:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我这腐坏的灵魂也不是一无是处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来很好吃吧？很想吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.47,0:17:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要一个能自由行动的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了夺取四魂之玉 并让桔梗成为我的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 吃吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.98,0:17:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后给我身体 给我力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都起源于鬼蜘蛛的邪念
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把身体交给聚集而来的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 妖怪奈落就诞生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 原来是那个山贼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还说四魂之玉被玷污后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会更加美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.51,0:18:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我和犬夜叉可悲地互相残杀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.95,0:18:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了得到被污染的玉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.75,0:18:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉也中了奈落的圈套 受了重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只不过是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想知道自己的死因罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 犬夜叉变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的表情变得温柔多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.04,0:18:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去他总是带着不相信任何人的执拗的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇是个不可思议的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.78,0:18:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在一点点地治愈犬夜叉的心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是那个女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她改变了犬夜叉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.72,0:18:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:19:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该由我来治愈犬夜叉的心的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.27,0:19:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是无法放弃对世间的迷恋吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.90,0:19:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您要在这世间徘徊到何时…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.35,0:20:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她回去了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.86,0:20:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得戈薇小姐那个样子很不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟桔梗小姐到底发生了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你总是跟女人做的那些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然在戈薇小姐面前做出那种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.64,0:20:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你平时到底在做什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇还会不会回来呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.48,0:20:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她好像下了很大的决心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来没有忘记过你！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.15,0:20:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那句话…是发自内心的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我与你亲吻的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.39,0:20:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是虚假的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她对我也是真心的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女人…比我重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.00,0:20:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 现在怎么办？犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.91,0:20:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗小姐应该还没走远
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.34,0:20:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要追她吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 戈薇比较重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.41,0:20:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 快点去跟戈薇和好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一时都昏了头 连行李都忘了带了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.96,0:21:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那上面有人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要怎么办？犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要选谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个都选行不行啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.87,0:21:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想脚踏两条船？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为男人我能了解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.55,0:21:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 就算撕裂你的嘴 都不能让她们本人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一被发现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.72,0:21:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 你就得坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.66,0:21:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就叫做天谴对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我觉得犬夜叉也没有什么恶意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.80,0:21:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}我们在生命的旅程中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}逐渐失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.77,0:22:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}仍坚信并追逐着光明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.77,0:22:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}现在与你一同启航
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.17,0:22:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}在那深深的丛林中 即使是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.67,0:22:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}也一定埋藏着被抛弃的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.50,0:22:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}若能操控时光的轮回
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.67,0:22:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}或许可以再次翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.32,0:22:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}我们一边迷茫彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.12,0:23:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}生存下去 直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}仍坚信并追逐着光明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.00,0:23:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}现在与你一同启航
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.29,0:23:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说附近有个除妖师的村庄
